must depend on the dealer, I think most states require it be registered but
vary on inforcement. fwiw I've rented dollies in Calif.,Oregon and British
Columbia, all they've ever cared about is the tow vehicle and what I'm
towing, just tell em I'm towing a bug and they go away happy.
Chuck
